      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Register to claim Erasmus+ and ESC funding from the government guarantee
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">If your organisation has a successful Erasmus+ or European Solidarity Corps (ESC) bid, register to claim against the government guarantee if there's a no-deal Brexit.</p>

  </div>
</div>

